<template>
  <el-table :data="tableData" stripe style="width: 100%">
    <el-table-column prop="price" label="Price" width="180"> </el-table-column>
    <el-table-column prop="time" label="Time" width="180"> </el-table-column>
    <!-- <el-table-column prop="name" label="Name" width="180"> </el-table-column> -->
    <!-- <el-table-column prop="address" label="Address"> </el-table-column> -->
  </el-table>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      props: { price: { type: Number }, time: { type: String } },
      tableData: [
        {
          price: 0,
        },
        {
          date: "2016-05-03",
          name: "Tom",
          address: "No. 189, Grove St, Los Angeles",
        },
        {
          date: "2016-05-02",
          name: "Tom",
          address: "No. 189, Grove St, Los Angeles",
        },
        {
          date: "2016-05-04",
          name: "Tom",
          address: "No. 189, Grove St, Los Angeles",
        },
        {
          date: "2016-05-01",
          name: "Tom",
          address: "No. 189, Grove St, Los Angeles",
        },
      ],
    };
  },
};
</script>
